twtoo or "twitter to tooter" is an app that brings Tweets to a Mastodon account.

How to install:
1. Install "twint" and "Mastodon.py"
2. Modify "config.py" to include the twitter account you want to mirror, the URL of your mastodon instance, and your mastodon username and password.
3. Run "register.py" in python3 to link this app and your user.
4. Run "loop.py" to start checking the target twitter account every 20 seconds.

Mastodon.py and twint copyright their respective owners

